      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a car of this age that has been driven with care. Inside, the cabin remains a clean, smoke-free environment. The leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in great shape; it starts immediately, idles quietly, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with the most recent oil change and brake inspection completed last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need a replacement anytime soon. This is a solid, honest car that looks great and drives even better.",
